# FANTASY FURLONG — ARCHITECTURE LOCK (v1.0)

Status: Locked  
Scope: Backend architecture, data flow, polling logic, database schema, API contracts  
UI intentionally excluded from this document.

- Phones never call Racing API directly.
- Worker is the only Racing API client.
- Web server reads/writes Postgres.
- UTC storage/comparison for all times.
- Idempotent scoring and settlement.
- Server-side pick locking by off_time.
- Snapshot odds freeze at 09:00.
- Leaderboard polling max every 15s.
